Create physical hdd file for use with virtual box. Run this command in cmd.exe window with admin rights whilst cd'ed into the VirtualBox program files folder, usually "C:\Program Files\Oracle\VirtualBox":

VBoxManage internalcommands createrawvmdk -filename "C:\Users\<user_name>\VirtualBox VMs\<VM_folder_name>\<file_name>.vmdk" -rawdisk \\.\PhysicalDrive#

